# PPTX Skill

Presentation creation, editing, and analysis for PowerPoint files.

## Creating Presentations (PptxGenJS)

```javascript
import PptxGenJS from "pptxgenjs";

const pptx = new PptxGenJS();
pptx.author = "Sigma Protocol";
pptx.title = "Project Overview";

// Title slide
const titleSlide = pptx.addSlide();
titleSlide.addText("Project Kickoff", {
  x: 0.5, y: 2.5, w: "90%",
  fontSize: 44, bold: true, color: "0F172A", align: "center",
});

// Content slide
const contentSlide = pptx.addSlide();
contentSlide.addText("Agenda", {
  x: 0.5, y: 1.0, fontSize: 32, bold: true,
});
contentSlide.addText([
  { text: "1. Project Overview", options: { bullet: true } },
  { text: "2. Timeline & Milestones", options: { bullet: true } },
  { text: "3. Next Steps", options: { bullet: true } },
], { x: 0.5, y: 2.0, w: "90%", fontSize: 18, lineSpacing: 28 });
```

## Adding Charts

```javascript
slide.addChart(pptx.ChartType.bar, [
  { name: "Revenue", labels: ["Q1", "Q2", "Q3"], values: [1200, 1500, 1800] },
  { name: "Costs", labels: ["Q1", "Q2", "Q3"], values: [800, 900, 1000] },
], { x: 0.5, y: 1.8, w: 9, h: 4.5, showLegend: true });
```

## Adding Tables

```javascript
slide.addTable([
  [{ text: "Feature", options: { bold: true, fill: { color: "0F172A" }, color: "FFFFFF" } },
   { text: "Basic", options: { bold: true, fill: { color: "0F172A" }, color: "FFFFFF" } },
   { text: "Pro", options: { bold: true, fill: { color: "0F172A" }, color: "FFFFFF" } }],
  ["Users", "5", "Unlimited"],
  ["Storage", "10 GB", "1 TB"],
], { x: 0.5, y: 1.8, w: 9 });
```

## Speaker Notes

```javascript
slide.addNotes("Key talking points:\n- Emphasize growth rate\n- Mention new clients");
```

## Design Best Practices

- Use consistent fonts (2-3 max)
- Limit colors to brand palette
- One main idea per slide
- 6x6 rule: Max 6 bullets, 6 words each
- Minimum 24pt font for body text
